    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>📅 Tuesday, September 16, 2025</strong><br><strong>A New Update Has Arrived: Card Pack Vol.9 “Omochi Chronicle” Now Available!</strong><br>From soothing voices to chaotic blades—<i>VTBattle: It’s Not About Subscribers—Decide It with Strength!</i> brings another exciting expansion to the battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This update adds <strong>35 new VTubers</strong>, pushing the total roster to <strong>over 300 unique creators</strong>. And who knows—you might even encounter a hidden character!?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🆕 What's New in Vol.9 “Omochi Chronicle”</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>35 new VTubers</strong> join the fray</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>New card type:</strong> <i>Chaos Edge</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>35 brand-new skills</strong> added to the system</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎀 Choose From Over 300 VTubers!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether they’re streamers, singers, illustrators, or ASMR talents, <strong>every single VTuber is fully playable as your main character</strong>.<br>Who will you bring to the battlefield?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139930/extras/b407ff2529ecf91d5ddda422504569bb.avif?t=1768307132\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139930/extras_big/b407ff2529ecf91d5ddda422504569bb.avif?t=1768307132 width=800 height=464 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📦 Build Your Collection!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over <strong>100 playable VTubers</strong>, each with <strong>multiple cards of varying rarities</strong>.<br>Strengthen your favorite creator’s deck and complete their collection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Strategic Card Game Meets Auto-Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a team of five cards to boost your stats—<strong>HP, ATK, DEF, MAG, MDEF, SPD</strong>—and challenge tougher opponents as you climb the ranks!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run feels different with roguelike elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outwit your opponents with strategic builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a wide variety of card effects and abilities</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139930/extras/13cfd1bb47e44ab16b225c7ecd7adcd6.avif?t=1768307132\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139930/extras_big/13cfd1bb47e44ab16b225c7ecd7adcd6.avif?t=1768307132 width=800 height=466 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💡 Every Card Can Be a Hero</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The strength of a card depends on its <strong>rarity, level, and synergy</strong>, not just the character.<br>Even low-rarity cards can become essential in the right build—<strong>every card matters</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⏱ Estimated Playtime</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single run takes <strong>1–2 hours</strong>, perfect for both casual sessions and intense theorycrafting.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📺 Streaming Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Monetization is allowed<br>✅ All scenes can be streamed<br>✅ VTBattle may be featured in full in videos or live streams</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📝 <i>Note:</i><br>Please be respectful to all participating VTubers. This game features real creators, and we ask for your support and kindness in your content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let us know who your favorite character is—and stay tuned for <strong>upcoming battle features and online modes</strong> in future updates!</p>",
